### Test EmailPush API

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7129

### 1. Get All Campaigns
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Campaigns

### 2. Create Campaign
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Campaigns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Welcome Campaign",
  "subject": "Welcome to our service!",
  "content": "Thank you for joining us. This is a test email campaign.",
  "recipients": ["user1@example.com", "user2@example.com", "user3@example.com"]
}

### 3. Get Campaign by ID (replace with actual ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Campaigns/{{campaignId}}

### 4. Start Campaign (replace with actual ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Campaigns/{{campaignId}}/start

### 5. Update Campaign (replace with actual ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Campaigns/{{campaignId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Campaign",
  "subject": "Updated Subject",
  "content": "This campaign has been updated.",
  "recipients": ["newuser@example.com"]
}

### 6. Delete Campaign (replace with actual ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Campaigns/{{campaignId}}